{"tid":1380148,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"同老闆講咗裸辭去讀書，但係依家唔捨得份人工，好後悔....","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:01:11.000Z","uid":73171,"like":0,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0f26e6c41757da05e63dd285adcb223c9181fd","tid":1380148,"uid":73171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:55:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我畢業兩年，係公司人工幾好，但係壓力好大，成日都好失落，開始覺得自己唔適合商業社會，想讀返書去大學做lecturer。<br />\n<br />\n諗左3個月，上個禮拜終於同老闆講話走，裸辭報master。我老闆都覺得我似係教書嘅人，對我走一啲都唔surprise，亦冇挽留我。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個weekend, 我開始覺得冇收入好不安，雖然屋企唔係等我養。我依家有啲後悔，驚未來10年搵唔返呢個人工。我未遞信，想同老闆講唔走而rotate去其他部門算，但係又驚自己好似好柒，講到自己好有自信去讀書但係倒頭來打倒昨日嘅自己。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好廢好無膽，唔想人生為錢而活但係又豁唔到出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位覺得我應該點樣做？"},{"pid":"018427632d0e10c7ba9b7d84d0f0db4298367489","tid":1380148,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜裸辭報master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月開既Master唔係一早截晒喇咩<br />\n同埋做Lecturer要Research Postgrad喎, 普通Taught Postgrad得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd2b2833379b7b5d24e8fc02995bb43409c1388","tid":1380148,"uid":73171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"018427632d0e10c7ba9b7d84d0f0db4298367489","tid":1380148,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜裸辭報master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月開既Master唔係一早截晒喇咩<br />\n同埋做Lecturer要Research Postgrad喎, 普通Taught Postgrad得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"我想九月開始報2020入學，依家返工太多嘢做，根本冇時間報<br />\n<br />\n我係想報MPhil呀～"},{"pid":"84f2c6a8016e3a6a41f2741f1acdc217103490d3","tid":1380148,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd2b2833379b7b5d24e8fc02995bb43409c1388","tid":1380